Description:
- And the Lord said : Let there be light ... naive to believe that this was the beginning . But no sooner was the beginning of all beginnings . And then , yes, a lot of things : the universe , wonderful garden, the tree of knowledge of good and evil triangle of Adam, Eve and Lilith , frenetic Methuselah , sword in hand , a revolt of the angels , the extermination of the dragons , the arrow in the heart of Cain , the deluge and extermination nefelimov , stokkimov and other giants ...
And ... the first in the world rainbow, a very important sign, the importance of which , alas, forgotten.
And three brave ... decided at any cost to reach the edge of the earth without fear of deadly dangers prepared for them at every turn. Let them tremble enemies , insidious evil wizards and evil , preparing for a meeting with the three of of Forests ! ..
And Gloom ... - Werewolf and the winner of the Gods - by accident and unknowingly erases the Genesis record of his death ...
And deceitful gods ... ...
And ... the secret society of the ancient sages - Secret Seven - administers the fate of the world ...
And ... What does it mean for Heroes dragons, magicians , wizards , witches , giants , along with his infamous might? After all, even the gods can find justice ! ...
...

- Say , familiar story ? No and no again ! After all - it's religious books in Russian science fiction , a kind of calling card Yuri Nikitin , one of the most popular and original writers of Russia .
